data.description:
All Offers Due by 4:00 PM on Tuesday 12/19/23!  Don't miss your chance to own this beautiful property!  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and the recent upgrades. The entire house features new luxury vinyl flooring, giving it a modern and fresh look. The bedrooms have been fitted with brand new carpeting, ensuring comfort and coziness. 
The kitchen is a true highlight of this home. It seamlessly flows into the spacious family room, creating an open and inviting space for gathering with loved ones. Imagine cozy evenings by the fireplace, creating lasting memories with friends and family.  
In addition to the family room, this house also offers a formal dining room and a formal living room, providing ample space for entertaining guests or hosting special occasions. The primary bedroom is a true retreat. It boasts an ensuite bathroom, offering privacy and convenience. With three bedrooms in total, there is plenty of space for everyone in the household. Convenience is key, as this property features main floor laundry facilities. No more hauling laundry up and down stairs!  The basement offers lots of space and ready for your finishing touch. Situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this property offers over an acre of land for all your outdoor activities. Whether you enjoy gardening or simply relaxing in nature, this expansive yard provides endless possibilities.

Don't wait any longer to make this Harper Creek beauty your own! Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort that this property has to offer.
